<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0073e6;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .token {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      word-break: break-word;
      max-width: 90%;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0073e6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        padding: 15px;
      }
      .token {
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        word-wrap: break-word;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Verify Your Account
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p>Your verification token is:</p>
      <p class="token">{{verificationToken}}</p>
      <p>If you did not create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@yourcompany.com">support@yourcompany.com</a>.</p>
      <p>Â© {{year}} Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
